1. Handling synchronisation/timing  issues
    wait for presence of an element
    Wait till element is enabled
    Wait till element is intractable
    Wait till <Condition>

    Never use Thread.sleep(waittime);
    Implicit wait (Global, work or presence of the element ) (Not recommended by experts ,Fail slowly )
    Explicit wait (Recommended, usually sufficient )
    Fluent wait (Advanced configuration )
    Custom wait
    Third party extensions/APIs (awaitability)

